1
00:00:00,420 --> 00:00:03,000
Is that your cute way of saying
you want to sleep together?

2
00:00:03,130 --> 00:00:05,010
No! Not at all!

3
00:00:07,090 --> 00:00:09,050
Oh, really?

4
00:00:09,760 --> 00:00:11,050
I'm tired too.

5
00:00:11,510 --> 00:00:12,260
I'm going to bed.

6
00:00:12,260 --> 00:00:13,260
I'm turning in first.

7
00:00:13,810 --> 00:00:14,890
Good night.

8
00:00:14,970 --> 00:00:15,970
Yeah.

9
00:00:18,310 --> 00:00:19,480
Hehe.

10
00:00:20,940 --> 00:00:23,190
(What did he mean, "continue later"?)

11
00:00:24,150 --> 00:00:25,360
(But still...)

12
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:28,450
(I guess he can't help it if he has work.)

13
00:00:34,280 --> 00:00:35,620
Honestly...

14
00:00:39,290 --> 00:00:40,830
Makoto?

15
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:44,380
Are you asleep?

16
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:46,130
(How could I possibly sleep?!)

17
00:00:46,130 --> 00:00:47,960
(I'm just pretending to be asleep.)

18
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:50,090
(I wish you'd think about me more!)

19
00:00:52,220 --> 00:00:53,960
I see.

20
00:00:54,930 --> 00:00:56,640
You're fast asleep.

21
00:01:03,020 --> 00:01:05,070
Thanks for coming all this way to see me.

22
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:14,160
(Oh no, what do I do now?)

23
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:16,450
(I completely missed my chance
to open my eyes.)

24
00:01:17,370 --> 00:01:18,410
So cute.

25
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:20,990
(This is bad.
I might not be able to hold back.)

26
00:01:22,290 --> 00:01:23,290
Ah!
